percentDvFootnote: Percent Daily Values are based on a 2,000 calorie diet.
targetGroups: Children 4 or More Years of Age

statements.notes:
Multivitamin with BCAA + Essential amino acids
Electrolytes + Natural B energy complex

Adults: Mix with 8 oz. of water of your favorite drink. Or, pour in mouth, let melt and then swallow. Take once daily, or, up to three times for enhanced benefits if you are: active, competing, tired or fighting illness.
Children (age 6+): 1/4 teaspoon daily.

Expect: It's possible to feel a warm, tingling sensation or flushing of skin due to Vitamin B-3 Niacin. Do not be alarmed - This feeling will pass in 15-20 minutes, if sensitive, take half servings for a few days.

statements.type: Precautions re: Pregnant or Nursing or Prescription Medications
statements.notes: If pregnant, it's recommended to also take a minimum of 400 mcg folate daily.
Sport formula is produced in a GMP certified lab
All ingredients meet USP standards and are WADA compliant (World Anti-Doping Agency).

Contains no banned substances.
No Additives
No preservatives
Ask your retailer for a sample of your other products or go to sportforumula.com/Sample

Sport formula is founded on nutrients that absorb.
All of our fresh, raw, powder nutrients are cold processed to maintain their live enzyme function and maximum bioavailability. This allows the receptor sites on your cells to attach to the nutrients in your bloodstream and be fully absorbed by your cells allowing your metabolism to fully function like it should. These are the keys to absorption. 
- Founder, Jimmy DiShanni
